n/columns/psbs-outperform-private-peers-yet-again-as-quarterly-profits-hit-new-high-126022200380_1.html","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-22T15:50:37","source":"Business Standard"},{"id":"260219157215952","title":"Kotak Mahindra Bank saw a 37.1% surge in derivatives open interest on 19 Feb 2026.\nDespite the spike, the stock underperformed its sector and broader indices.","summary":"Kotak Mahindra Bank saw a 37.1% surge in derivatives open interest on 19 Feb 2026.\nDespite the spike, the stock underperformed its sector and broader indices.","url":"https://www.marketsmojo.com/news/stocks-in-action/kotak-mahindra-bank-sees-sharp-surge-in-derivatives-open-interest-amid-mixed-price-action-3847291","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-19T15:00:29","source":"Marketsmojo"},{"id":"260219156810893","title":"New M&A funding norms present $15B opportunity for banks with strong investment banking capabilities.\nKey changes include 75% acquisition financing, 3:1 debt-equity ratio, and doubled finance cap to 20% of Tier 1 capital.","summary":"New M&A funding norms present $15B opportunity for banks with strong investment banking capabilities.\nKey changes include 75% acquisition financing, 3:1 debt-equity ratio, and doubled finance cap to 20% of Tier 1 capital.","url":"https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/markets/stocks/news/ma-funding-norms-open-up-a-15-b-opportunity-for-banks/articleshow/128532445.cms","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-19T00:00:00","source":"The Economic Times"},{"id":"502270","title":"Kotak Mahindra Bank appoints Ramesh Iyer as Independent Director for 4 years from Feb 17, 2026, succeeding Dr. Ashok Gulati.\nIyer, with over 40 years in Mahindra Group, has held key roles and won multiple industry awards like Ernst & Young Entrepreneur of the Year.","summary":"Kotak Mahindra Bank appoints Ramesh Iyer as Independent Director for 4 years from Feb 17, 2026, succeeding Dr. Ashok Gulati.\nIyer, with over 40 years in Mahindra Group, has held key roles and won multiple industry awards like Ernst & Young Entrepreneur of the Year.","url":"https://www.cnbctv18.com/business/companies/kotak-mahindra-bank-appoints-ramesh-iyer-as-independent-director-ashok-gulati-to-retire-in-march-ws-l-19852338.htm","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-17T22:48:12","source":"CNBC TV 18"},{"id":"260215154330483","title":"RBI's revised guidelines on acquisition financing enable Indian banks like SBI, Bank of India, and Kotak Mahindra Bank to participate in M&A, refinancing, and stake hikes with eased equity requirements.\nThe new norms allow unlisted firms with Rs 500 crore net worth and 3-year profitability to access financing, boosting domestic consolidation and capex in sectors like manufacturing and healthcare.","summary":"RBI's revised guidelines on acquisition financing enable Indian banks like SBI, Bank of India, and Kotak Mahindra Bank to participate in M&A, refinancing, and stake hikes with eased equity requirements.\nThe new norms allow unlisted firms with Rs 500 crore net worth and 3-year profitability to access financing, boosting domestic consolidation and capex in sectors like manufacturing and healthcare.","url":"https://www.financialexpress.com/business/banking-finance/banks-to-drive-domestic-mampa-as-rbi-eases-financing-norms/4143843/","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-15T19:07:00","source":"Financial Express"},{"id":"493053","title":"Kotak Mahindra Bank executed Rs. 103.3 crore NSE block trade for 2,459,567 shares.\nThe trade occurred at Rs. 420 per share, reflecting significant transaction volume.","summary":"Kotak Mahindra Bank executed Rs. 103.3 crore NSE block trade for 2,459,567 shares.\nThe trade occurred at Rs. 420 per share, reflecting significant transaction volume.","url":"","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-13T14:48:37","source":"Livesquawk"},{"id":"260209150298186","title":"Kotak Mahindra Bank CTO Bhavnish Lathia resigns citing personal reasons.\nNilesh Chaudhari takes over as CTO; Lathia's last day was February 9.","summary":"Kotak Mahindra Bank CTO Bhavnish Lathia resigns citing personal reasons.\nNilesh Chaudhari takes over as CTO; Lathia's last day was February 9.","url":"https://www.business-standard.com/companies/people/kotak-bank-cto-bhavnish-lathia-resigns-nilesh-chaudhari-appointed-126020901550_1.html","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-09T21:25:13","source":"Business Standard"},{"id":"480680","title":"Kotak Mahindra Bank to meet investors at Axis Capital's Advantage India Conference on Feb 12, 2026.\nThe meeting is disclosed under SEBI Regulation 30 for investor information and dissemination.","summary":"Kotak Mahindra Bank to meet investors at Axis Capital's Advantage India Conference on Feb 12, 2026.\nThe meeting is disclosed under SEBI Regulation 30 for investor information and dissemination.","url":"https://www.bseindia.com/stockinfo/AnnPdfOpen.aspx?Pname=4015d95f-361e-43e3-83d5-4fc461796b1b.pdf","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-09T18:09:09","source":"BSE"},{"id":"479027","title":"DICGC will adopt risk-based deposit insurance premiums from April 2026, benefiting large banks like HDFC Bank, ICICI Bank, Axis Bank, and Kotak Mahindra Bank with lower operating expenses.\nPremium reductions could cut operating expenses by 1.5-3% and boost earnings by 1-2% for private banks, with PSU banks potentially benefiting from higher ratings.","summary":"DICGC will adopt risk-based deposit insurance premiums from April 2026, benefiting large banks like HDFC Bank, ICICI Bank, Axis Bank, and Kotak Mahindra Bank with lower operating expenses.\nPremium reductions could cut operating expenses by 1.5-3% and boost earnings by 1-2% for private banks, with PSU banks potentially benefiting from higher ratings.","url":"https://www.cnbctv18.com/market/deposit-insurance-premiums-explainer-why-psu-banks-are-hot-shares-price-ws-l-19845291.htm","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-09T10:19:45","source":"CNBC TV 18"},{"id":"477167","title":"DIPAM receives financial bids for IDBI Bank privatisation, targeting sale of 60.72% stake worth ₹72,000 crore.\nKotak Mahindra Bank, Fairfax India Holdings emerge as contenders; announcement expected by March 2026.","summary":"DIPAM receives financial bids for IDBI Bank privatisation, targeting sale of 60.72% stake worth ₹72,000 crore.\nKotak Mahindra Bank, Fairfax India Holdings emerge as contenders; announcement expected by March 2026.","url":"https://www.cnbctv18.com/business/companies/kotak-mahindra-bank-fairfax-emerge-as-bidders-for-idbi-bank-stake-sale-19844557.htm","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-06T20:59:54","source":"CNBC TV 18"},{"id":"474720","title":"Kotak Mahindra Bank saw an NSE block trade of 2,782,768 shares at Rs. 412.3.\nThe total trade value for this transaction amounted to Rs. 114.73 crores.","summary":"Kotak Mahindra Bank saw an NSE block trade of 2,782,768 shares at Rs. 412.3.\nThe total trade value for this transaction amounted to Rs. 114.73 crores.","url":"","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-06T09:28:02","source":"Livesquawk"},{"id":"260206148210863","title":"Kotak Mahindra and Fairfax to submit separate financial bids for IDBI stake.\nThey aim to acquire 60.72% stake held by the government and LIC.","summary":"Kotak Mahindra and Fairfax to submit separate financial bids for IDBI stake.\nThey aim to acquire 60.72% stake held by the government and LIC.","url":"https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/industry/banking/finance/banking/idbi-stake-sale-kotak-mahindra-fairfax-to-submit-financial-bids/articleshow/127950731.cms","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-06T00:00:00","source":"The Economic Times"},{"id":"462519","title":"IDBI Bank's privatization enters final stage; final bids due by Feb 5. Kotak Mahindra, Emirates NBD, and Fairfax India are shortlisted.\nGovt and LIC to sell over 60% stake; bid price to follow SEBI takeover rules. Winner may be identified by March 2026.","summary":"IDBI Bank's privatization enters final stage; final bids due by Feb 5. Kotak Mahindra, Emirates NBD, and Fairfax India are shortlisted.\nGovt and LIC to sell over 60% stake; bid price to follow SEBI takeover rules. Winner may be identified by March 2026.","url":"https://hindi.moneycontrol.com/news/business/idbi-bank-stake-sale-dipam-asked-shortlisted-bidders-to-place-final-bids-by-february-5-2356074.html","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-30T22:48:26","source":"Money Control"},{"id":"455801","title":"Kotak Mahindra Bank executed an NSE block trade of 2M+ shares at Rs. 410.6.\nThe transaction totaled Rs. 82.8 crores.","summary":"Kotak Mahindra Bank executed an NSE block trade of 2M+ shares at Rs. 410.6.\nThe transaction totaled Rs. 82.8 crores.","url":"","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-28T10:25:24","source":"Livesquawk"},{"id":"454852","title":"Axis Bank surged 5%, overtaking Kotak Mahindra Bank in market cap after strong earnings.\nCiti upgraded Axis Bank, setting a target price of ₹1,463, citing growth visibility.","summary":"Axis Bank surged 5%, overtaking Kotak Mahindra Bank in market cap after strong earnings.\nCiti upgraded Axis Bank, setting a target price of ₹1,463, citing growth visibility.","url":"https://www.cnbctv18.com/market/axis-bank-overtakes-kotak-mahindra-bank-to-become-third-largest-private-lender-by-market-cap-ws-l-19834118.htm","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-27T17:18:19","source":"CNBC TV 18"}]}]